\date{2024-08-03}
\title{Zero objects from (co)-slice}
\taxon{proposition}
\import{macros}

\p{The [slice category](math-005X) #{\cat{C}/0} over the [initial object](math-0052) has a zero object.}

\p{Likewise, the co-[slice category](math-005X) #{1/\cat{C}} under the [terminal object](math-001G) has a zero object.}